# CODEOWNERS
# 
# This file defines code ownership for the SubZero repository.
# GitHub will automatically request reviews from these owners when PRs modify their areas.
#
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# === Global Default ===
# Chief of Staff reviews everything by default
